\\\\\" OR \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"talent acquisition\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\") (intern OR \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"new grad\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" OR SWE OR software) LinkedIn -inurl:jobs`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  - `\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"<Company>\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Recruiter at <Company>\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" OR \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"University Recruiter at <Company>\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" site:linkedin.com/in`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  - `\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"<Company>\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" (recruiter OR \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"talent partner\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" OR \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"hiring\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\") (internship OR \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"campus recruiting\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" OR \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"university hiring\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\") 2025 OR 2026`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n## Required Start Status Command\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n```bash\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nnode -e '\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nconst fs=require(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"fs\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"); const d=JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"job/sectors/recruiter-retail.json\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"utf8\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"));\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nconst companies=d.companies||[];\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nconst unpop=companies.filter(c=>!(c.recruiters||[]).length);\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nconst missing=companies.filter(c=>!String(c.description||\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\").trim());\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nconst under10=companies.filter(c=>(c.recruiters||[]).length<10);\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nconst phase=(unpop.length||missing.length) ? \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"coverage\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" : (under10.length ? \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"bolster\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" : \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"expand\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\");\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nconsole.log(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"=== SECTOR retail STATUS ===\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\");\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nconsole.log(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"File: job/sectors/recruiter-retail.json\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\");\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nconsole.log(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Phase:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", phase, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"| Companies:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", companies.length, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"| Unpopulated:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", unpop.length, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"| Missing descriptions:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", missing.length, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"| Below 10 contacts:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", under10.length);\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nconsole.log(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Recruiters:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", companies.reduce((s,c)=>s+(c.recruiters||[]).length,0));\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nconsole.log(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Next work:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\");\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n[...unpop, ...missing.filter(c=>!unpop.some(u=>u.id===c.id)), ...under10.filter(c=>!unpop.some(u=>u.id===c.id)&&!missing.some(m=>m.id===c.id))]\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  .sort((a,b)=>(a.priority-b.priority)||a.id.localeCompare(b.id))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  .slice(0,14)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  .forEach(c=>console.log(c.id, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"P\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"+c.priority, c.name, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"| recs=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"+((c.recruiters||[]).length), \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"| desc=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"+(String(c.description||\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\").trim() ? \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"yes\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" : \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"no\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\")));\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n'\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n```\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n