ative AI applications across business workflows.',\n    hq_location: 'Boston, MA',\n    careers_url: 'https://www.datarobot.com/careers/',\n    linkedin_url_verified: true,\n    recruiters: [\n      {\n        name: 'Ariel M.',\n        title: 'Talent Acquisition Lead',\n        linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/ariel-m-8341754b',\n        email: '',\n        location: 'Los Angeles Metropolitan Area',\n        focus_area: 'R&D hiring and AI talent acquisition',\n        connected: false,\n        messaged: false,\n        responded: false,\n        date_contacted: '',\n        notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile identifies Ariel as a DataRobot Talent Acquisition Lead specializing in R&D hiring.'\n      },\n      {\n        name: 'Nelson P. Sousa, Jr.',\n        title: 'People Business Partner / HR Leader',\n        linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/nelsonsousajr',\n        email: '',\n        location: 'White Plains, NY',\n        focus_area: 'People leadership and GTM recruiting support',\n        connected: false,\n        messaged: false,\n        responded: false,\n        date_contacted: '',\n        notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile shows current DataRobot people role; public activity promotes DataRobot Senior Recruiter hiring.'\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  C0683: {\n    description: 'H2O.ai builds open-source and enterprise AI platforms for predictive, generative, agentic, and sovereign AI applications across regulated industries and public sector teams.',\n    hq_location: 'Mountain View, CA',\n    careers_url: 'https://h2o.ai/company/careers/',\n    linkedin_url_verified: true,\n    recruiters: [\n      {\n        name: 'Adam Lee',\n        title: 'Talent Acquisition',\n        linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/adam-lee-0277b52b',\n        email: '',\n        location: 'Pensacola, FL',\n        focus_area: 'Talent acquisition for AI and technology roles',\n        connected: false,\n        messaged: false,\n        responded: false,\n     