rk across large codebases and enterprise development workflows.',\n    hq_location: 'San Francisco, CA',\n    recruiter: {\n      name: 'Scott Wu',\n      title: 'Co-founder and CEO, Cognition',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/scott-wu-8b94ab96',\n      email: '',\n      location: 'San Francisco, CA, United States',\n      focus_area: 'AI software agents, engineering leadership, technical hiring',\n      connected: false,\n      messaged: false,\n      responded: false,\n      date_contacted: '',\n      notes: 'Public sources identify Wu as Cognition co-founder and CEO; included as technical hiring and leadership contact for a thin public recruiting signal.'\n    }\n  },\n  C0733: {\n    description: 'Magic trains frontier code models with long-context memory to build AI coworkers that assist with software engineering and research tasks.',\n    hq_location: 'San Francisco, CA',\n    recruiter: {\n      name: 'Mark Horton',\n      title: 'Head of People, Magic',\n      linkedin_url: '',\n      email: '',\n      location: 'United States',\n      focus_area: 'People operations, technical recruiting, AI research hiring',\n      connected: false,\n      messaged: false,\n      responded: false,\n      date_contacted: '',\n      notes: 'Public org data and LinkedIn activity identify Horton as Head of People at Magic; Magic careers activity shows active ML, CUDA, infrastructure, and research hiring.'\n    }\n  },\n  C0735: {\n    description: 'Codeium, now Windsurf, builds AI-powered developer tools and an agentic IDE that help engineers write, navigate, and automate code.',\n    hq_location: 'Mountain View, CA',\n    linkedin_company_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/windsurf123321',\n    recruiter_search_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/people/?keywords=Windsurf%20Codeium%20recruiter',\n    recruiter: {\n      name: 'Jeff Wang',\n      title: 'CEO, Windsurf (formerly Codeium)',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/jefflinw