 Intelligence, now part of Cisco, secures AI applications by testing model vulnerabilities and enforcing guardrails against safety and security threats.',\n    hq_location: 'San Francisco, CA',\n    recruiter: {\n      name: 'Yaron Singer',\n      title: 'VP, AI and Security at Cisco; Co-founder and former CEO, Robust Intelligence',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/yaron-singer-76ab6317',\n      email: '',\n      location: 'San Francisco, CA, United States',\n      focus_area: 'AI security, model risk, security engineering leadership',\n      connected: false,\n      messaged: false,\n      responded: false,\n      date_contacted: '',\n      notes: 'Public LinkedIn and company sources identify Singer as Robust Intelligence founder/CEO and Cisco AI/security leader after the acquisition.'\n    }\n  }\n};\nlet touched = 0;\nlet added = 0;\nfor (const company of data.companies || []) {\n  const update = updates[company.id];\n  if (\"'!update) continue;\n  touched++;\n  company.description = update.description;\n  if (update.hq_location) company.hq_location = update.hq_location;\n  if (update.linkedin_company_url) company.linkedin_company_url = update.linkedin_company_url;\n  if (update.recruiter_search_url) company.recruiter_search_url = update.recruiter_search_url;\n  company.linkedin_url_verified = true;\n  company.careers_url = company.careers_url || '\"'';\n  const recruiters = company.recruiters || [];\n  const exists = recruiters.some(r => r.name === update.recruiter.name || (update.recruiter.linkedin_url && r.linkedin_url === update.recruiter.linkedin_url));\n  if (\"'!exists) {\n    recruiters.push(update.recruiter);\n    added++;\n  }\n  company.recruiters = recruiters;\n}\nif (touched !== Object.keys(updates).length) {\n  throw new Error(`Expected to touch ${Object.keys(updates).length}, touched ${touched}`);\n}\nfs.writeFileSync(path, JSON.stringify(data, null, 2) + '\"'\\\\n');\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify({ touched, added }, null, 2));\nNODE